lockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁，之前仲要買左成打芯，點撚支成盒芯都係咁撚樣，寫寫下就冇墨，之後仲要斷埋。<br />\nP.S 冇跌過支筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2341a20065bc1e39b2e7394bb1dc853b28ec63cc","tid":95970,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有冇巴打覺得jet stream 原裝筆芯好順好好寫<br />\n<br />\n但替芯就有問題，一開始都好順，但寫寫下就好似斷左墨咁，寫出黎既字又幼又淺色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到唔敢再用<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係咁，之前仲要買左成打芯，點撚支成盒芯都係咁撚樣，寫寫下就冇墨，之後仲要斷埋。<br />\nP.S 冇跌過支筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊轉用sarasa啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c245be8174937095be04b3699a1563ff8e2b815d","tid":95970,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ce8fvk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCe8fvk0.jpg&h=7152aae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢支都好寫<br />\n好順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係D墨用得好快, 之前買左枝用左兩個禮拜冇晒墨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa34070e0611117d2ac3c030188c478e95a9bfc","tid":95970,"uid":8976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高登神筆Jetstream <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外G2都唔錯 只要你唔好手賤跌筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nG2依家唔跌筆都會無墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />質素差左好多"},{"pid":"2ab118aa